===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[radical]] [[ion]]'''
#{{chemistry}} any radical that also carries an [[electric]] [[charge]]; typically, the charge and [[unpaired electron]] are associated with the same [[atom]]
===Usage notes===
*They are represented with a dot, either before or after the plus or minus sign e.g. C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>6</sub><sup>.+</sup> or C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>6</sub><sup>+.</sup>
